<paragraph blockId="36.[807,1422,241,293]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">
<emphasis box="[807,932,241,262]" italics="true" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">Etymology.</emphasis>
Latin for hairy, referring to the lateral setation of the ovipositor.
</paragraph>
